➜慢0.5秒差14万元！国产电车现在这么刚了？比亚迪汉/唐福州上市
http://www.sohu.com/a/416664295_99994080	59140
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200906/37c1c6ee6a654429ba2819fec05334c1.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200906/e8e5982524604b62983793bd82e3f140.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>本文编辑</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200906/650a6d117eee49ea8bb931f7e107562a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>写在前面：</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
